   <standOff>
      <listAnnotation type="typednotes" xml:lang="nl">
         <note xml:id="note.d433e10036" type="dating">
            <p>Enveloppe. Poststempel: zaterdag 19 december 1914.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
      <listAnnotation type="typednotes" xml:lang="en">
         <note xml:id="note.d433e10110" type="dating">
            <p>Envelope. Postmark: Saturday 19 December 1914.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
      <listAnnotation type="notes" xml:lang="nl">
         <note n="1" xml:id="note.orig.nl.1">
            <p>
               <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers128">Vincent</rs> had een blindedarmoperatie moeten ondergaan, waardoor zijn huwelijk met <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers078">Josina Wibaut</rs> was uitgesteld. Jo aan Clémentine Elisa Marguerite Gachet. VGM, b3452; 5 januari 1915.</p>
         </note>
         <note n="2" xml:id="note.orig.nl.2">
            <p>Het is niet met zekerheid te zeggen om welk portret het gaat. Mogelijk ging het om Isaac Israëls, <hi rend="italics">Jo van Gogh-Bonger</hi>, ongedateerd (mogelijk 1915). <rs type="artwork" ref="artwork.xml#ii023">Ill. ii023</rs> Zie ook brief <ref target="ii070.xml">070</ref> en <ref target="ii071.xml">071</ref>.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
      <listAnnotation type="notes" xml:lang="en">
         <note n="1" xml:id="note.tr.en.1">
            <p>
               <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers128">Vincent</rs> had had an appendectomy, so his wedding to <rs type="person" ref="bio.xml#pers078">Josina Wibaut</rs> had to be postponed. Jo to Clémentine Elisa Marguerite Gachet. VGM, b3452; 5 January 1915.</p>
         </note>
         <note n="2" xml:id="note.tr.en.2">
            <p>It is not possible to say for certain which portrait this was. It may have been Isaac Israëls, <hi rend="italics">Jo van Gogh-Bonger</hi>, undated (possibly 1915). <rs type="artwork" ref="artwork.xml#ii023">Ill. ii023</rs> See also letters <ref target="ii070.xml">070</ref> and <ref target="ii071.xml">071</ref>.</p>
         </note>
      </listAnnotation>
